Invocation Name: cloud services
des:
This skill uses the Amazon Web Services FAQ data to answer you questions about a particular service.
You can invoke a service by saying- Alexa, open cloud services.
Then, you will be asked to select from which service you want to ask a question. you can say something like - Amazon EC2.
Then you can ask the question, like- "what is amazon ec2?" OR "What is Amazon ec2 auto scaling group?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
